Cell["\<\
For demonstration, consider a three-qubit system, and an arbitrary unitary \
operation on it.\
\>", "TechNoteText",
 CellID->1917505328,ExpressionUUID->"4d81427a-406d-4db4-b8b2-801055256f27"],

